    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>arborio rice </strong>and <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and cook for 1 min or until the Chinese rice wine has evaporated</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1660041117545-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1660041117545-x400.jpg",
